By":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:14:55.000Z","msg":"唔拉<br />\n唔告<br />\n破唔到案<br />\n<br />\n既加埋係幾多 ？"},{"pid":"e135f9bd5d90d3611c612adeec04cf0d98e9ca2c","tid":1001284,"uid":31749,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:16:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1e572f0f4941cf9cef826b9fe8be5e96ea4dab4","tid":1001284,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>罪案係少左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n警隊反而有上升係咩玩法&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我9錢十年前已經屌，用分數計，黑犬自己刑罪率高過16歲以上市民，近年甚至高過黑社會！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">岩岩打去PPRB@28606144，問警隊自己都認舊年刑罪率高過整體市民幾倍有乜回應...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有隻時沙答官方對仍有99.8%冇犯法好撚驕傲bababa！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>咁好彩打得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nPPRB 99.9%時間唔通 閉門做車</blockquote>得99.8炸? <br />\n港鐵咁撚無恥搞到民怨四起都話有99.9準時率<br />\n你而家先得99.8，知唔知個醜字點寫<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c305abdf4053b8b856046f59f4e72fb21149389b","tid":1001284,"uid":140769,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid